text: Damian Gardiner (23 September 1968 - 10 September 2013) was an Irish equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. Gardiner died of cancer, aged 44. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:2013 deaths Category:Irish male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Ireland Category:Equestrians at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
